reviewText: This vhs is in great condition! They don't make Playboy videos like this anymore. It's a shame that Playboy won't take the older videos and laserdiscs (from the 80's) and transfer them to a dvd. Thank goodness that vcr's still exist. I'm glad to have found this tape on Amazon because I couldn't find it on ebay. Thank you Amazon for this classic 80's Playboy video:-)

Playmates include Hope Marie Carlton (July 1985, 36-22-32), Devin DeVasquez (June 1985, 34-22-34), Patty Duffek (May 1984, 36-23-32), Lourdes Estores (June 1982, 34-22-33), Kim Evenson (September 1984, 36-25-35), Kymberly Herrin (March 1981, 36-24-36), Debi Johnson (October 1984, 35-21-34), Kimberly McArthur (January 1982, 37-22-34), Donna Smith (March 1985, 37-24-35), Dona Spier (March 1984, 37-24-35), Liz Stewart (July 1984, 35-23-34), Roberta Vasquez (November 1984, 40-25-36) and Lynda Weismeier (July 1982, 36-22-36), all frolicking and competing in little and sometimes next to nothing on a warm, sunny SoCal day. What more could you ask for?
